name: arangodb_transaction_memory_rest
introducedIn: "3.12.0"
help: |
  Global value of accumulated memory consumption for REST transactions.
unit: number
type: gauge
category: RocksDB
complexity: advanced
exposedBy:
  - dbserver
  - coordinator
  - agent
  - single
description: |
  This metric reflects the current amount of memory in bytes consumed by 
transactions in arangod.  Either a used managed transaction, or a 
transaction that was triggered by a user command are the transactions that 
contribute to the increase/decrease of this value.
~                                                                                                                                           
~                                                                                                                                           
~                                                                                                                                           
~                                           
